### Welcome endpoint
GET http://localhost:8000/
Accept: application/json

### Create a new Todo
POST http://localhost:8000/todos
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Learn Deno",
  "description": "Master Deno and Oak framework"
}

### Create a second Todo
POST http://localhost:8000/todos
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Build REST API",
  "description": "Create a complete CRUD API with Deno"
}

### Get all Todos
GET http://localhost:8000/todos
Accept: application/json

### Get all Todos with pagination
GET http://localhost:8000/todos?page=1&limit=5
Accept: application/json

### Get Todo by ID (replace with actual ID after creating)
GET http://localhost:8000/todos/5411f94f-f2de-4c1e-ae85-145cd7576ae8
Accept: application/json

### Update Todo (replace with actual ID after creating)
PUT http://localhost:8000/todos/5411f94f-f2de-4c1e-ae85-145cd7576ae8
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Learn Deno - Updated",
  "description": "Master Deno and Oak framework with advanced features",
  "completed": true
}

### Update Todo completion status only
PUT http://localhost:8000/todos/5411f94f-f2de-4c1e-ae85-145cd7576ae8
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "completed": true
}

### Delete Todo by ID (replace with actual ID after creating)
DELETE http://localhost:8000/todos/5411f94f-f2de-4c1e-ae85-145cd7576ae8

### Delete all Todos
DELETE http://localhost:8000/todos